{
  "stem": "26447.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We cannot say all of them is bad or all of them is good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, most of them become bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we, well, that's what they was doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then another night, they come to me and take from me, give give up the money what you got.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They was-- they know what I was working for a, know that's in the government business, and I got the money, government money.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At night time, give up the money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I give up all the money what I got.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They asked me, give-- you have-- you have a gun, or you have-- I say I never got a gun, and I don't have now to.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was not in the army that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I don't know how to use the gun.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I never got.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No, that was only-- only to more, to bring some conflicts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, and that-- we stayed like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every day is a new-- new-- new-- new problems to take our seats.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a lot, a lot, a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's-- I forgot a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, to tell you only the episodes, the short episodes, it's un-possible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Every day it was problems.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the problems with we got for a couple months what we stay in the village Komarow, decided the-- their head of their-- when the German came, the head of the village said we need to put-- to take, use-- the German tell to the ghetto, take us to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, into the ghetto, we didn't take-- we didn't got what to take.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They tell us, you can take only the food if you want.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "No-- was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We take what we can-- we-- what we take, most of them, a little food what we got.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
